```plantuml
@startuml ruoccofabrizio_azure-open-ai-embeddings-qna

actor User
participant "Streamlit Web App" as WebApp
participant "Azure OpenAI" as OpenAI
participant "Vector Store" as VectorStore
participant "Azure Functions" as Functions
participant "Azure Queue" as Queue
participant "Azure Blob Storage" as BlobStorage

User -> WebApp: Submit Question
WebApp -> OpenAI: Generate Embedding (Question)
OpenAI --> WebApp: Return Question Embedding
WebApp -> VectorStore: Search Similar Documents
VectorStore --> WebApp: Return Relevant Chunks
WebApp -> OpenAI: Generate Answer (Question + Chunks)
OpenAI --> WebApp: Return Generated Answer
WebApp --> User: Display Answer

group Batch Processing
User -> Functions: Trigger Batch Process (HTTP)
Functions -> Queue: Add Processing Message
Queue -> Functions: Trigger Processing Function
Functions -> BlobStorage: Retrieve Documents
Functions -> OpenAI: Generate Embeddings (Documents)
OpenAI --> Functions: Return Document Embeddings
Functions -> VectorStore: Store Document Embeddings
end

@enduml
```